item.title: BarCamp Photos
item.description: You’ll find photos of the day in two main locations: Pix.ie Flickr Some of the snappers include: Phil O’Kane Alexia Golez Donncha O’Caoimh Jessica Mannering Me In general if you are uploading pics, please tag them with “barcampcork” so we can find them on the various sites. Leave a comment below with a direct link to your pics.
